[2026-03-26T20:37:28.914489] [TOOL_CALL] [write_blackboard] args=() kwargs={'key': 'architecture', 'value': 'Architecture v1.1 - Updated to align with feature_list and actual implementation.\n\nFiles:\n- output/architecture/c4_context.md (Level 1: System Context)\n- output/architecture/c4_containers.md (Level 2: Containers - React SPA, FastAPI Backend, SQLite)\n- output/architecture/c4_components.md (Level 3: Components - detailed backend & frontend components)\n- output/architecture/architecture_overview.md (Full overview with ADRs, data flows, security)\n- output/shared_dependencies.json v1.1.0 (Updated interface contracts matching actual implementation)\n\nStack: FastAPI + SQLite + SQLAlchemy + React 18 + Vite\nAuth: JWT (python-jose) + bcrypt (direct)\nAPI: REST with auto Swagger docs at /docs\n\nActual Backend structure: app/main.py, app/config.py, app/database.py, app/models.py, app/schemas.py, app/auth.py, app/routers/{auth_router,task_router,dashboard_router}.py\nFrontend structure: src/main.jsx, src/App.jsx, src/api/, src/context/, src/hooks/, src/pages/, src/components/\n\nEndpoints: POST /api/auth/register (201), POST /api/auth/login (200), GET /api/auth/me (200), GET /api/tasks/ (200, with filters), POST /api/tasks/ (201), GET/PUT/DELETE /api/tasks/{id}, GET /api/dashboard/stats (200), GET /health\n\nModels: User (id, username, email, hashed_password, created_at), Task (id, title, description, priority, status, due_date, owner_id, created_at, updated_at)\nEnums: TaskPriority(low/medium/high), TaskStatus(todo/in_progress/done)\n\nKNOWN ISSUES:\n- ISSUE-001 (HIGH): Login uses username instead of email (feature_list F-002 requires email)\n- ISSUE-002 (MEDIUM): Duplicate registration returns 400 instead of 409 (feature_list F-001 requires 409)'}
